verbose_text: Predicted ribbon structures were aligned along the dimerization plane and are presented as homodimers, and further to previously published work regarding the energetic feasibility of PI5P4Kalpha-PI5P4Kbeta heterodimers [XREF_BIBR], our modelling also suggests that the dimerization interface would support PI5P4Kalpha-PI5P4Kgamma and PI5P4Kbeta-PI5P4Kgamma heterodimers, with predicted number and lengths of potential hydrogen bonds similar to homodimer structures (XREF_TABLE).
